            "type": "text",
            "text": "For EU-resident personal data, the legal basis for any cross-border transfer to a third country (including the US) must be established before processing occurs. This is separate from the technical routing question — even if data physically stays in the EU endpoint, the data processing relationship between your organization and Anthropic must be covered by an appropriate legal mechanism."
          }
